<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ສະເໜີຂາຍລົດ (เสนอขายรถ / 提供出售汽車)</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Phetsarath+OT:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="bg-dark text-gold">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center py-3">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h1>ສະເໜີຂາຍລົດຂອງທ່ານ (เสนอขายรถของคุณ / 出售您的汽車)</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-end">
                    <a href="/trade-in" class="btn btn-maroon">Trade-in your car (แลกเปลี่ยนรถของคุณ / 交換您的汽車)</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-black">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 50px;">
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">ໜ້າຫຼັກ (หน้าแรก / 首頁)</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/sell-car">ສະເໜີຂາຍລົດ (เสนอขายรถ / 提供出售汽車)</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">ຕິດຕໍ່ (ติดต่อ / 聯繫)</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h2 class="text-center">ສະເໜີຂາຍລົດ (เสนอขายรถ / 提供出售汽車)</h2>
        <form action="/sell-car" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="brand" class="form-label">ຍີ່ຫໍ້ (ยี่ห้อ / 品牌)</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="brand" name="brand" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="model" class="form-label">ຮຸ່ນ (รุ่น / 型號)</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="model" name="model" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="year" class="form-label">ປີ (ปี / 年份)</label>
                <input type="number" class="form-control" id="year" name="year" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="price" class="form-label">ລາຄາ (ราคา / 價格)</label>
                <input type="number" class="form-control" id="price" name="price" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="color" class="form-label">ສີ (สี / 顏色)</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="color" name="color" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="location" class="form-label">ສະຖານທີ່ (สถานที่ / 地點)</label>
                <select class="form-control" id="location" name="location" required>
                    <% provinces.forEach(province => { %>
                        <option value="<%- province %>"><%- province %></option>
                    <% }) %>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="images" class="form-label">ຮູບພາບລົດ (รูปภาพรถ / 汽車圖片)</label>
                <input type="file" class="form-control" id="images" name="images" multiple accept="image/*">
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">ສົ່ງຄຳຂໍ (ส่งคำขอ / 提交請求)</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer bg-black text-gold mt-4">
        <div class="container py-4">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ (ข้อมูลเพิ่มเติม / 更多信息)</h5>
                    <p>ຕະຫຼາດລົດອອນໄລນ໌ Chobrod.com ເພີ່ມທາງເລືອກໃຫ້ທ່ານຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ (ตลาดรถออนไลน์ Chobrod.com เพิ่มทางเลือกให้คุณมากขึ้น / Chobrod.com 在線汽車市場為您提供更多選擇)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>ຕິດຕໍ່ (ติดต่อ / 聯繫)</h5>
                    <p>ອີເມວ: contact@yourcarwebsite.com (อีเมล: contact@yourcarwebsite.com / 電子郵件: contact@yourcarwebsite.com)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>ຕິດຕາມ (ติดตาม / 跟隨)</h5>
                    <p>Facebook, TikTok (Facebook, TikTok / Facebook, TikTok)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-center mt-4">© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ (สงวนลิขสิทธิ์ / 版權所有)</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>